A series of implementations of use cases that address some requirements of human-aware planning.

All problems are minimal and self-contained.

Solve a problem by running one of the following commands from SpiderPlan root:

Social Acceptability:

	./run.sh domains/human-aware-planning-use-cases/planner.spider domains/human-aware-planning-use-cases/social-acceptability/use-case-1.uddl
	./run.sh domains/human-aware-planning-use-cases/planner.spider domains/human-aware-planning-use-cases/social-acceptability/use-case-2.uddl 
	./run.sh domains/human-aware-planning-use-cases/planner.spider domains/human-aware-planning-use-cases/social-acceptability/use-case-3.uddl  

Proactive:

	./run.sh domains/human-aware-planning-use-cases/planner.spider domains/human-aware-planning-use-cases/proactivity/use-case-1.uddl
	./run.sh domains/human-aware-planning-use-cases/planner.spider domains/human-aware-planning-use-cases/proactivity/use-case-2.uddl 
	./run.sh domains/human-aware-planning-use-cases/planner.spider domains/human-aware-planning-use-cases/proactivity/use-case-3.uddl  

Context Awareness:

	./run.sh domains/human-aware-planning-use-cases/planner.spider domains/human-aware-planning-use-cases/context-awareness/use-case-1.uddl 
	./run.sh domains/human-aware-planning-use-cases/planner.spider domains/human-aware-planning-use-cases/context-awareness/use-case-2.uddl 
	./run.sh domains/human-aware-planning-use-cases/planner.spider domains/human-aware-planning-use-cases/context-awareness/use-case-3.uddl 
	./run.sh domains/human-aware-planning-use-cases/planner.spider domains/human-aware-planning-use-cases/context-awareness/use-case-4.uddl 